1.3
log
@instead of using the 'total' summary from the wc command, calculate the sum directly ourselves using a simple sum function. this slows things down considerably, but is necessary to avoid the default behavior of xargs on linux that can break up a piped stream into multiple invocations (resulting in multiple total lines).
@
text
@a81 1

d90 2
d98 2
d106 2
d114 2
d122 2
d134 1
d144 1
@


